message.body: Hey Lo, is it alright to invite Hugo to the milonga portion of our rehearsal tomorrow?
Ya, I'm Gonna work on the show for a few hours tonight, you might need to send me a reminder to tell you when I schedule that part
Any word on when milonga will be in the schedule so i can let hugo know?
Oh boy, I Judy spent several hours making a graph of people, pieces and requests of all kinds. Still need to add to It, was gonna wake up real early and do the rest. Should we just say 3?
